arrayGenerator

Class ListingGeneratorTest

  • java.lang.Object
    • arrayGenerator.ArrayGeneratorTest
      • arrayGenerator.ListingGeneratorTest
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    RandomListingGeneratorTest, SortedListingGeneratorTest

    abstract class ListingGeneratorTest
extends ArrayGeneratorTest
    A tester class for ListingGenerators. This class inherits the array size tester method and tests from ArrayGeneratorTest, and defines a new test method and some tests that check that the generated array does indeed contain the values 0..n-1.
    Version:
    September 2020
    Author:
    Hugh Osborne

    • Method Detail

      • testContents

        public void testContents(int size)
        Test the contents of this listing. A listing of size n must contain all of the values from 0 to n-1 (and each value muse, consequently, appear exactly once).
        Parameters:
        size - the size of listing to be generated and tested.
